1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: New life, first day of school. Ella, her brother Guy and her friend Omar are starting high school. They all start the day with the right foot, until a handsome guy comes, and he was especially looking for Ella. At lunch brake ( or something) there was smoke (gas) in the hallway. with everyone in panic, and nobody seeing anything, Ella got kidnapped. After she was saved by Leo (the handsome guy) a new life with problems, nightmare and vampires is waiting to kill both teenagers
